{"tid":111204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 九龍灣天橋底發現可疑人骨　重案接手查","createTime":"2017-02-07T08:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T09:02:11.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75d5ed4a3bc43ac7bf3f92c25a83900aea85fc7e","tid":111204,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:57:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170207/bkn-20170207120446489-0207_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170207%2Fbkn-20170207120446489-0207_00822_001.html&d=BZ3h%2BuUaIL2OU9i9OZdAr10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=24afa8b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170207/bkn-20170207120446489-0207_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">九龍灣天橋底發現可疑人骨　重案接手查</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170207/photo/bkn-20170207120446489-0207_00822_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170207%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170207120446489-0207_00822_001_01b.jpg&h=65d73ddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【14：45】發現骸骨的女工返回現場，指出發現骸骨位置，同時有探員走上橋面調查及拋下物件，測試是否可能有人由橋面墮下。警方在場架設帳篷，鑑證科人員穿着保護袍搜證。<br />\n<br />\n【13:00】警方調查後，在現場發現一件T恤及外套，由於死者的骸骨不完整，未能確定死者的身份，將案件轉交重案組跟進，以追查死因是否有可疑。<br />\n<br />\n九龍灣偉業街德福花園對開橋底驚見懷疑人體骸骨。早上10時許，兩名食環署外判工人在上址行車天橋底一帶負責剪草，期間驚見花槽內懷疑有一具人體骸骨，頭顱有帽遮蓋着，大驚下報警求助。警方接報趕至，封鎖現場及偉業街東行一段慢線進行調查。"},{"pid":"e17feecbcadcc901cc45d217c725d1b5039c26e2","tid":111204,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T08:59:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170207/photo/bkn-20170207120446489-0207_00822_001_10b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170207%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170207120446489-0207_00822_001_10b.jpg&h=9d6e42a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170207/photo/bkn-20170207120446489-0207_00822_001_09b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170207%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170207120446489-0207_00822_001_09b.jpg&h=de0f9fc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170207/photo/bkn-20170207120446489-0207_00822_001_11b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170207%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170207120446489-0207_00822_001_11b.jpg&h=8a1556e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170207/photo/bkn-20170207120446489-0207_00822_001_08b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170207%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170207120446489-0207_00822_001_08b.jpg&h=c9748b80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170207/photo/bkn-20170207120446489-0207_00822_001_05b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170207%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170207120446489-0207_00822_001_05b.jpg&h=383b6cd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8123354cfe5e274902b78a164b9a674d4a2809fd","tid":111204,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:02:11.000Z","msg":"看肛洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}